---
// src/components/sections/HowToStart.astro
---
<section class="px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">How to Start a Journaling Practice</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Every experienced journaler started exactly where you are now: staring at a blank notebook with good intentions and no idea what to write.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-1xl p-8 shadow-sm mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
      <span class="bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm">01</span>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Choose Your Format First</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">Before you think about what to write, decide where to write. The best format is whichever one you will actually use consistently.</p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Paper -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-indigo-600">
            <span class="font-bold">Paper Journaling</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>• Feels more personal and private</li>
          <li>• Handwriting activates different neural pathways</li>
          <li>• Tactile experience slows you down</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- Digital -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-emerald-600">
            <span class="font-bold">Digital Journaling</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>• Faster, more searchable, always accessible</li>
          <li>• Password-protected privacy</li>
          <li>• Apps offer prompts and mood tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <!-- Step 02, 03, 04 cards logic same as above -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mb-4 block">02</span>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Start Smaller Than Necessary</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Three sentences. That's it. "What is on my mind right now?"</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Step 03 & 04 can be added similarly -->
  </div>
</section>